query:
-- Primeiro, identificar o produto do endereço H01-01-01
SELECT 
  i.productId,
  p.sku,
  p.description,
  i.batch,
  i.reservedQuantity
FROM inventory i
INNER JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
INNER JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
WHERE wl.code = 'H01-01-01'
  AND i.reservedQuantity > 0
LIMIT 1;
